{"type": "excalidraw", "version": 2, "source": "excalidraw-diagram-skill", "elements": [{"type": "rectangle", "id": "darkbg", "x": -4000, "y": -3000, "width": 10000, "height": 7500, "backgroundColor": "#1e1e2e", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "transparent", "strokeWidth": 0, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100}, {"type": "text", "id": "title1", "x": 20, "y": 10, "width": 550, "height": 28, "text": "Step 1 (환경 설치)", "fontSize": 20, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "box2", "x": 20, "y": 45, "width": 550.0, "height": 624, "backgroundColor": "#1e3a5f", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4a9eed", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt3", "x": 35, "y": 60, "width": 520, "height": 594, "text": "→ Step 2 (JS 복습) → Step 3 (생태계) → Step 4 (JSX)\n▼\nStep 5 (Props) → Step 6 (useState) → Step 7 (Reconciliation)\n▼  ▼\nStep 11 (useEffect)  Step 9 (리스트)\n▼  ▼\nStep 8 (Form)  Step 12 (useRef) → Step 13 (useReducer)\n▼\nStep 14 (메모이제이션) → Step 16 (Custom Hook)\n▼\nStep 15 (신규 Hooks) → Step 10 (내부 구조)\n▼\nStep 18 (Router) → Step 19 (렌더링 전략)\n▼  ▼\nStep 22 (패칭)  Step 20 (RSC) → Step 21 (Next.js)\n▼\nStep 23 (TanStack Query) → Step 24 (상태 경계)\n▼\nStep 25 (Context) → Step 26 (전역 상태) → Step 27 (아키텍처)\n▼\nStep 28 (폴더 구조) → Step 29 (컴포넌트 패턴) → Step 30 (Suspense)\n▼\nStep 31~35 (타입/폼/스타일/애니메이션)\n▼\nStep 36~38 (테스트/접근성/성능)\n▼\nStep 39~42 (빌드/배포/CI·CD/보안)", "fontSize": 14, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100, "containerId": "box2"}], "appState": {"viewBackgroundColor": "#1e1e2e"}}